* Managed vs\nExternal Volumes
** Managed volumes
***_ Unity Catalog manages storage & lifecycle
***_ Files deleted after 7-day retention on drop
***_ Best for Databricks-only workflows
** External volumes
***_ Specify storage path on create
***_ Drop = remove registration only
***_ Files remain in cloud storage
***_ Best for multi-system data sharing
** Both
***_ Same path format for access
***_ Same permissions model
***_ Can use /Volumes/... path
@endmindmap
